Hello,
I would like to request support for this Tuya Zigbee wall switch:

ModelId: TS0012

ManufacturerName: _TZ3000_e98krvvk

Type: 2‑gang wall switch (two physical relays)

Added as: Unknown Zigbee Device in Homey Pro 2023

Below is the full Zigbee interview.

Important note about this device:
Although the Zigbee interview exposes only one standard On/Off output cluster, this specific TS0012 unit has two physical relays:

Left button → controls “Entrada” (load 1)

Right button → controls “Vestíbulo” (load 2)

The second relay appears to be handled through Tuya private clusters (57344 / 57345) instead of a standard endpoint/output cluster.

This is a known behavior in some TS0012 variants with glass touch panels.

